ğŸ“Œ Problem Statement

Employees and HR departments in Saudi Arabia face difficulties accessing accurate and clear information on local labor laws due to:
- Complex legal language  
- Scattered and hard-to-access official sources  
- High costs of legal consultations  

ğŸš¨ Consequences:
- Misunderstanding of rights and obligations  
- Financial risks and penalties  
- Wasted time and costly manual research  

