ğŸš€ How to Run Locally

1. Install dependencies  
   pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Build the FAISS index  
   python app/build_index.py

3. Run the backend  
   uvicorn app.main:app --reload

4. Open the frontend  
   Open frontend/index.html in your browser.

